                        <div class="messageMenu"> <!-- messages are in reverse order, so we can flex-reverse and start the scroll at the bottom -->
                            <messageBubble class="msgFromOther">
                                For something like that, the usual price is $1,000
                            </messageBubble>
                            <messageBubble class="msgFromOther">
                                We can take the weight as we're moving, but if it's less than 500 pounds...
