                            </messageBubble>
                            <messageBubble class="msgFromOther">
                                It sounds like we will be able to fit everything in one load in one truck, but if we need additional trips or trucks, it'll be more.
                            </messageBubble>
                            <messageBubble class="msgFromOther">
                                It would depend on the total weight, and the distance between locations.
                            </messageBubble>
                            <messageBubble class="msgFromUser">
                                I'm wanting to move some of the stuff in my home to a storage unit. It's a desk, dresser, a table, and a few other smaller things. The dresser is pretty heavy, but the desk and table aren't too bad. What would be the price for something like that?
                            </messageBubble>
                            <messageBubble class="msgFromOther">
                                How much are you trying to move?
                            </messageBubble>
                            <messageBubble class="msgFromUser">
                                Hey, I saw your posting, what would the cost be?
                            </messageBubble>
